    <div class="row mt-5 mb-5">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <h2>About Daily Farm System</h2>
            <img src="images/The-cow.jpg" alt="The Cow">
            <p>The appliacation aim at tracking daily activites of a daily farm with a view to enhance productivity and manage cost.</p>

